286
00:18:23,554 --> 00:18:25,025
Brother, you see...

287
00:18:27,516 --> 00:18:29,017
About Jaemin...

288
00:18:29,935 --> 00:18:31,128
I think he's a bit strange.

289
00:18:31,854 --> 00:18:33,143
I never told anyone that

290
00:18:33,157 --> 00:18:34,837
I was working there.

291
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,649
Him suddenly showing up like that

292
00:18:36,674 --> 00:18:37,700
was strange.

293
00:18:37,949 --> 00:18:39,075
And the fact that

294
00:18:40,083 --> 00:18:42,085
he appeared right after I got hurt.

295
00:18:43,532 --> 00:18:44,972
It doesn't feel like a coincidence.

296
00:18:48,370 --> 00:18:50,471
The amount you mentioned is different.

297
00:18:51,165 --> 00:18:52,916
You should have done as instructed.

298
00:18:54,293 --> 00:18:55,853
I only told you to scare her.

299
00:18:55,878 --> 00:18:57,191
The one who caused the injury

300
00:18:57,218 --> 00:18:58,477
and made things complicated

301
00:19:00,591 --> 00:19:02,003
was you, wasn't it?

302
00:19:14,605 --> 00:19:15,817
What do you mean by that?

303
00:19:16,940 --> 00:19:18,584
It's like...

304
00:19:18,609 --> 00:19:20,944
He had anticipated everything.

305
00:19:21,445 --> 00:19:22,629
That can't be.

306
00:19:22,654 --> 00:19:23,929
You know that too.

307
00:19:24,662 --> 00:19:26,206
You know how much he looks after us.

308
00:19:27,534 --> 00:19:28,823
It's just a coincidence.

309
00:19:32,143 --> 00:19:33,091
Sorry.

310
00:19:33,099 --> 00:19:34,625
Maybe I'm just being too sensitive.

311
00:19:43,258 --> 00:19:44,259
Oh, right.

312
00:19:44,683 --> 00:19:46,547
The person who came with you earlier...

313
00:19:50,025 --> 00:19:51,611
Never mind, it's nothing.

314
00:20:07,007 --> 00:20:08,749
I'm Daon's younger sister.

315
00:20:09,319 --> 00:20:11,022
Can I see you for a moment?

316
00:20:20,712 --> 00:20:22,126
Over here.

317
00:20:32,182 --> 00:20:33,934
The guardian for patient Jung Dasul?

318
00:20:35,259 --> 00:20:36,697
My guardian isn't coming.

319
00:20:37,145 --> 00:20:38,455
- Why?
- Oh.

320
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,206
I have to explain about wound cleaning.

321
00:20:40,466 --> 00:20:42,044
When will the guardian be here?

322
00:20:45,009 --> 00:20:46,385
I'm here.

323
00:20:47,489 --> 00:20:48,737
You are...

324
00:20:49,241 --> 00:20:50,811
I'm Daon's coworker.

325
00:20:51,743 --> 00:20:53,387
Is the wound serious?

326
00:20:53,412 --> 00:20:54,712
Not too bad, but she needs to

327
00:20:54,725 --> 00:20:56,416
clean it properly to avoid scarring.

328
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,512
Scarring?

329
00:20:57,532 --> 00:20:59,352
Is the wound deep enough
to leave a scar?

330
00:20:59,376 --> 00:21:00,644
There's no damage to the bone, right?

331
00:21:00,669 --> 00:21:01,997
Yes, there's no issue.

332
00:21:03,380 --> 00:21:04,660
The medication should be taken

333
00:21:04,667 --> 00:21:06,027
three times a day after meals.

334
00:21:06,967 --> 00:21:08,053
This is a scar ointment,

335
00:21:08,078 --> 00:21:09,244
apply it regularly.

336
00:21:11,054 --> 00:21:13,181
This is a heat pack.

337
00:21:15,475 --> 00:21:17,978
Here's some water and snacks.

338
00:21:19,646 --> 00:21:21,398
I also got slippers, just in case.

339
00:21:22,941 --> 00:21:24,014
I found your number in

340
00:21:24,021 --> 00:21:25,281
the guardian contact section

341
00:21:25,301 --> 00:21:26,354
and called you.

342
00:21:26,695 --> 00:21:28,589
Sorry for asking to meet so suddenly.

343
00:21:28,614 --> 00:21:29,793
It's fine.

344
00:21:33,243 --> 00:21:36,896
How much did all of that cost?

345
00:21:36,921 --> 00:21:39,124
- I'll pay you back.
- I didn't buy them expecting repayment.

346
00:21:39,124 --> 00:21:40,781
It doesn't sit right with me.

347
00:21:47,591 --> 00:21:49,364
You remind me of your brother.

348
00:21:49,885 --> 00:21:51,746
I wanted to help, so I did.

349
00:21:52,054 --> 00:21:53,263
You don't have to pay me back.

350
00:21:54,056 --> 00:21:56,141
But if it really bothers you...

351
00:21:58,038 --> 00:21:59,081
Then do this instead.

352
00:22:11,448 --> 00:22:13,007
Do you like my brother?

353
00:22:16,411 --> 00:22:17,579
Ah, well...

354
00:22:18,497 --> 00:22:19,865
My brother has a ridiculously

355
00:22:19,890 --> 00:22:21,363
strong sense of pride.

356
00:22:21,541 --> 00:22:22,668
And he's extremely stubborn.

357
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:24,503
Sometimes, I wonder if he's my brother.

358
00:22:24,503 --> 00:22:25,886
Because he likes to say things

359
00:22:25,911 --> 00:22:27,271
without thinking.

360
00:22:28,572 --> 00:22:29,782
But...

361
00:22:30,384 --> 00:22:31,802
He doesn't mean any of it.

362
00:22:32,970 --> 00:22:35,889
So, even if he acts like an idiot...

363
00:22:36,556 --> 00:22:38,196
Don't give up on him.

364
00:22:38,642 --> 00:22:40,452
If you stay by his side,

365
00:22:40,484 --> 00:22:41,986
he'll open his heart eventually.

366
00:23:17,889 --> 00:23:19,182
I told you not to come.

367
00:23:21,601 --> 00:23:23,196
I have something to talk to you about

368
00:23:23,223 --> 00:23:24,316
regarding your sister.

369
00:23:24,896 --> 00:23:26,359
There was no guardian yesterday,

370
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:27,839
so I got the explanation instead.

371
00:23:28,066 --> 00:23:30,276
- You should know as well...
- I'll take care of it.

372
00:23:31,111 --> 00:23:32,237
Don't worry about it.

373
00:23:34,614 --> 00:23:36,283
How can I not worry?

374
00:23:36,992 --> 00:23:38,140
Why?

375
00:23:38,623 --> 00:23:40,328
Do you feel too sorry for me
to ignore it?

376
00:23:40,328 --> 00:23:41,596
It's not like that.

377
00:23:41,627 --> 00:23:44,189
- I've never thought of you as pitiful.
- I'm embarrassed!

378
00:24:01,647 --> 00:24:02,982
What's so embarrassing about it?

379
00:24:03,489 --> 00:24:04,622
I've shown you even more

380
00:24:04,629 --> 00:24:05,969
embarrassing sides of myself.

381
00:24:07,189 --> 00:24:09,579
Begging, pleading, clinging to you...

382
00:24:10,275 --> 00:24:12,282
I've shown you all my lowest points.

383
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,868
So just stop it.

384
00:24:15,075 --> 00:24:16,262
You don't have to try so hard

385
00:24:16,276 --> 00:24:17,252
to be by my side.

386
00:24:17,277 --> 00:24:18,862
But I can't stop, what should I do?

387
00:24:20,911 --> 00:24:22,395
I hate that I'm like this.

388
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:23,860
I feel so pathetic and humiliated

389
00:24:23,885 --> 00:24:24,920
that I just want to die.

390
00:24:25,832 --> 00:24:27,476
But

391
00:24:27,501 --> 00:24:28,514
I just can't let go,

392
00:24:28,534 --> 00:24:29,634
no matter what I do!

393
00:24:32,534 --> 00:24:33,948
Every day is hell.

394
00:24:35,092 --> 00:24:36,592
I pretend to be fine in front of you,

395
00:24:36,599 --> 00:24:38,425
but my heart shatters hundreds of times.

396
00:24:39,179 --> 00:24:40,189
I said I'd wait,

397
00:24:40,214 --> 00:24:41,527
but what if you never come?

398
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,412
I was so scared that

399
00:24:43,426 --> 00:24:44,459
I couldn't do anything.

400
00:24:49,564 --> 00:24:51,009
So...

401
00:24:53,854 --> 00:24:55,767
Can't you just like me back?

402
00:25:01,243 --> 00:25:02,953
If you tell me not to come, I won't.

403
00:25:04,204 --> 00:25:05,712
If you say you don't want to see me,

404
00:25:05,737 --> 00:25:06,737
I'll hide.

405
00:25:08,166 --> 00:25:10,001
But please, don't abandon me.

406
00:25:12,838 --> 00:25:15,072
Promise me you won't leave me behind.

407
00:25:19,845 --> 00:25:21,470
No matter how long it takes, I'll wait.

408
00:25:22,264 --> 00:25:23,482
Okay?

409
00:26:28,002 --> 00:26:29,587
What did you want to say?

410
00:26:42,344 --> 00:26:43,797
Why are you giving me this?

411
00:26:44,262 --> 00:26:45,282
You said you'd accept

412
00:26:45,295 --> 00:26:46,532
if I gave you a ring.

413
00:26:46,605 --> 00:26:47,837
When did I ever say that?

414
00:26:47,862 --> 00:26:50,281
Then, if I buy one, will you take it?

415
00:26:50,602 --> 00:26:52,273
Alright. I'll take it.

416
00:26:57,859 --> 00:26:59,252
This is how I feel.

417
00:27:00,849 --> 00:27:02,442
Back then, and even now.

418
00:27:04,115 --> 00:27:05,283
It's always been you.

419
00:27:17,087 --> 00:27:18,338
Let's start over.

420
00:27:19,881 --> 00:27:21,508
I promise I'll never leave again.

421
00:27:27,013 --> 00:27:28,723
So please, don't abandon me.

422
00:27:31,649 --> 00:27:33,367
Promise me you won't leave me behind.

423
00:27:55,875 --> 00:27:57,296
I can't go back.

424
00:28:01,047 --> 00:28:02,507
Too much time has passed.

425
00:28:03,675 --> 00:28:05,427
It's too late to return.

426
00:28:09,848 --> 00:28:11,190
Now I understand.

427
00:28:13,518 --> 00:28:15,004
No matter how much regret comes

428
00:28:15,018 --> 00:28:16,163
after losing something,

429
00:28:16,187 --> 00:28:17,480
it's useless.

430
00:28:20,367 --> 00:28:21,868
I'm not going to run away anymore.

431
00:28:25,305 --> 00:28:26,410
I am...

432
00:28:27,907 --> 00:28:29,284
going to follow my heart.

433
00:28:43,548 --> 00:28:44,924
Where are you right now,
Assistant Manager Ju?

434
00:28:45,383 --> 00:28:46,804
I have something to say.

435
00:28:47,591 --> 00:28:48,737
No.

436
00:28:48,762 --> 00:28:50,030
You can't.

437
00:28:50,055 --> 00:28:51,883
You can't do whatever you want.

438
00:28:54,392 --> 00:28:55,649
Let go.

439
00:28:55,821 --> 00:28:57,214
You think everything will be fine

440
00:28:57,239 --> 00:28:58,291
if I just step aside?

441
00:28:58,903 --> 00:29:00,748
Take care of Shin Jaemin first.

442
00:29:02,484 --> 00:29:04,062
The real problem isn't me.

443
00:29:04,361 --> 00:29:05,684
It's that bastard, Shin Jaemin.

444
00:29:07,947 --> 00:29:09,240
The thing that Park Junghoon

445
00:29:09,265 --> 00:29:10,305
did to you...

446
00:29:10,544 --> 00:29:11,604
The reason I had to go

447
00:29:11,625 --> 00:29:13,095
to that overseas program...

448
00:29:13,119 --> 00:29:15,001
Everything that happened to you...

449
00:29:15,872 --> 00:29:16,985
It was all orchestrated by

450
00:29:16,992 --> 00:29:18,100
Shin Jaemin behind the scenes.

451
00:29:18,125 --> 00:29:19,507
That can't be true.

452
00:29:20,143 --> 00:29:21,227
Jaemin hyung would never...

453
00:29:21,258 --> 00:29:22,593
About Jaemin...

454
00:29:23,291 --> 00:29:24,647
I think he's a bit strange.

455
00:29:24,672 --> 00:29:25,985
I never told anyone that

456
00:29:25,992 --> 00:29:27,672
I was working there.

457
00:29:27,967 --> 00:29:29,173
Him suddenly showing up like that

458
00:29:29,194 --> 00:29:30,001
was strange.

459
00:29:30,033 --> 00:29:31,664
And the fact that

460
00:29:32,013 --> 00:29:33,932
he appeared right after I got hurt.

461
00:29:34,391 --> 00:29:35,891
It doesn't feel like a coincidence.

462
00:29:42,690 --> 00:29:44,859
Are you free to meet, hyung?

463
00:29:45,263 --> 00:29:46,775
Do you want to come over to my place?

464
00:30:16,391 --> 00:30:17,641
Come in.

465
00:30:18,685 --> 00:30:19,883
You haven't eaten yet, right?

466
00:30:20,353 --> 00:30:21,891
Let's eat together.

467
00:30:22,063 --> 00:30:23,440
I made pasta too.

468
00:30:26,025 --> 00:30:27,235
Come on, sit down.

469
00:30:28,361 --> 00:30:29,462
Was it you, hyung?

470
00:30:31,114 --> 00:30:32,449
Did you do that to Dasul?

471
00:30:34,159 --> 00:30:35,455
Was it really you?

472
00:30:37,704 --> 00:30:39,080
What are you talking about, Daon?

473
00:30:39,289 --> 00:30:41,015
The thing with Park Junghoon,

474
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:43,156
sending Suhyeon hyung abroad,

475
00:30:44,002 --> 00:30:45,429
was that all your doing?

476
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:55,058
Yeah.

477
00:30:56,931 --> 00:30:58,321
I did it.

478
00:30:59,267 --> 00:31:00,298
Why?

479
00:31:02,298 --> 00:31:04,024
Is that not allowed?

480
00:31:04,444 --> 00:31:06,407
- Why?
- Because I love you.

481
00:31:08,526 --> 00:31:09,944
I did it all for you.

482
00:31:11,779 --> 00:31:13,388
You did it because

483
00:31:13,717 --> 00:31:15,001
you love me?

484
00:31:16,284 --> 00:31:17,857
That doesn't make it right!

485
00:31:45,939 --> 00:31:47,398
Let's talk again later.

486
00:32:08,595 --> 00:32:09,790
Hyung!

487
00:32:59,429 --> 00:33:00,530
Tell me.

488
00:33:00,575 --> 00:33:01,595
Which part of my face

489
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:02,662
is the most handsome?

490
00:33:03,766 --> 00:33:05,977
No, I wasn't looking at your face.

491
00:33:08,771 --> 00:33:10,539
I was looking at the ring on your hand.

492
00:33:11,075 --> 00:33:12,271
The ring?

493
00:33:14,235 --> 00:33:15,403
If you like it, you can have it.

494
00:33:17,203 --> 00:33:18,781
Umm, no.

495
00:33:22,991 --> 00:33:24,554
But...

496
00:33:24,579 --> 00:33:26,280
how much does a ring like that cost?

497
00:33:26,914 --> 00:33:28,195
This? Not much.

498
00:33:29,208 --> 00:33:30,405
About ten million won?

499
00:33:31,794 --> 00:33:33,325
Ten million won?

500
00:33:34,464 --> 00:33:35,714
Don't worry, I won't ask you

501
00:33:35,734 --> 00:33:36,747
to buy me one.

502
00:33:38,259 --> 00:33:40,011
Why would I buy a ring for you, hyung?

503
00:33:47,101 --> 00:33:48,411
Then...

504
00:33:48,436 --> 00:33:49,979
if I buy it for you, will you take it?

505
00:33:52,732 --> 00:33:54,167
Should I just go home?

506
00:33:54,192 --> 00:33:55,278
What? You've been here less

507
00:33:55,292 --> 00:33:56,086
than ten minutes.

508
00:33:56,110 --> 00:33:57,575
Someone's coming.

509
00:34:02,617 --> 00:34:04,406
Alright. I'll take it.
